<ol>
  <li>A loaf of your favorite bread</li>
  <li>Extra-large eggs, because you want a generous yolk.</li>
  <li>Your favorite bacon</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="steps">Steps</h2>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Fry Your Bacon in a Skillet</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Reduce the Heat as the Bacon Starts to Sizzle</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Use Bacon Fat to Fry Your Eggs</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>The Temperature of the Fat is Important</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Use Hearty Bread for Toast</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Baste Your Eggs with Bacon Fat</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Blot the Eggs Before Serving</p>
  </li>
</ol>

